Technology Hardware, Storage and Peripherals

Company Overview of Savage IO, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Savage IO, Inc. designs, manufactures, and sells data storage systems. The company’s hardware products include data storage and graphics processing unit based servers. It also offers infrastructure as a service, a method of handling technological infrastructure needs using a third party host and operates hardware, servers, software, storage, and other infrastructure related needs in a cloud for a company. In addition, the company runs mining operations for multiple different currencies, including bitcoin, ethereum, and other digital currencies. Savage IO, Inc. was founded in 2011 and is based in Fairport, New York.


45 Connor RoadFairport, NY 14450United StatesFounded in 2011



