Mining Services

Get the latest S9 Bitcoin miner with 13.5 TH/s hash rate hosted in Savage IO’s world class facility to maximize profit and return on investment. 


                                                Know More                                            






Savage IO – Big Data Storage, Currency Mining, and Computing Hardware

Savage IO is a leader in providing services and equipment to others who wish to mine the different forms of currency and providing the infrastructure needed for those who require a fast turnaround (low latency) from a large set of stored data. 


                                                Know More                                            





 






Mining Services 
Get the latest S9 Bitcoin miner with 13.5 TH/s hash rate hosted in Savage IO’s world class facility to maximize profit and return on investment. 







                                                                View More                                                            








 






Infrastructure as a Service (IaaS) 
You have a lot of data. You need fast response (low latency) access to your data. You might, for example, have interests in gaming, security, currency mining, investment trading, or other applications that require a fast turnaround with big data. You can look to SIO to provide storage of information needing fast calculations and turnaround. The SIO Information as a Service (IaaS) service provides secure, private storage of high quantities of data that you can access at a speed that will let you compete or trade and profit at any time. 







                                                                View More                                                            








 






Hardware 
Savage IO specializes in data storage and GPU based servers. We focus on aggressively maximizing the performance of our hardware. Our goal is to provide you with the fastest turnaround hardware at your site or in your remote rented facility.







